---
/**
 * Slide 07 · employer-and-district-partnerships — 550+ schools across 10 states.
 * Source: src/content/messages/employer-and-district-partnerships.md
 */
const id = 'partnerships';

const states = ['CA', 'AL', 'AR', 'GA', 'LA', 'CO', 'MS', 'TX', 'TN', 'WA'];
---

<section id={id} class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 vibrant:bg-black snap-start">
  <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-xs tracking-widest text-gray-400 dark:text-slate-500 vibrant:text-orange-500/80 font-mono">07 / 09</span>

  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-6">Partnerships</p>

  <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-tight max-w-4xl mb-12">
    Hundreds of employers grow specialized talent from inside their own workforce.
  </h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-6xl mb-16">
    <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-700 dark:border-blue-400 vibrant:border-orange-500 pl-6">
      <p class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-none">550<span class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 vibrant:text-orange-500">+</span></p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-stone-300 mt-3">school partners</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 dark:border-slate-600 vibrant:border-orange-500/40 pl-6">
      <p class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-none">10</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-stone-300 mt-3">states</p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {states.map((s) => (
          <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 px-2 py-1 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 vibrant:border-orange-500/30 rounded-sm bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 vibrant:bg-slate-950">{s}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 vibrant:border-orange-500/30 pt-8">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">Three operating regions</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">California, the Southeast, and a dedicated Behavioral Health region — each with its own VP of Impact.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">The partner ask is light</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">Post materials, host info sessions, allow 15 hrs/week of academic-classroom time, designate a liaison.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-orange-400 mb-2">Productivity rises during the degree</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-200 leading-relaxed">Candidates apply learning to the workplace the same week they study it — not after graduation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
